  "rich_text": [
    "ElNet COD Transfer switch controller/generator",
    "The Elant COD system is designed for an effective exchange between two power supply sources (power company / generator) when one of them fails, the system is more reliable than any other replacement system and saves the installation of command and delay relays and lack of voltage relays, switches, voltmeters, etc.\nThe Elant COD system includes a friendly screen in the Hebrew language that enables, among other things, the following actions:\n- The display of system indications in the Hebrew language\n- Simple and efficient installation and wiring.\n– Installation on DIN rail.\n- Perfect protection for the generator (Double Interlock), one internal to the controller and one external.\n- Changing parameters and timers and more.",
    "Related Products",
    "Control Applications Ltd",
